Jennifer White Shah also known as Jenny White is a British actress.
She played Julia Livilla in The Caesars and also appeared in the original Casino Royale film and in Carry on Doctor.She is married to Eddy Shah.

response: Shah is married to actress Jennifer White Shah, whom he first met while he was working for Granada Television. The company was producing The Caesars (1968) and Jennifer White was an actress playing Caligula's sister in the series. They have three children, and live in Chippenham.
*Jennifer White Shah, or Jenny White, British actress and businesswoman
